                                            <h5>Source: Principal Economics based on Cabinet papers (MfE, 2021).<a href="https://6229.freelancedeveloper.site/impact-of-the-factors-of-supply#source-principal-economics-based-on-cabinet-papers-mfe-2021." class="anchor-section" aria-label="Anchor link to header"></a></h5>
